snippet.title: Celeste coming to Nintendo Switch!
snippet.description:
From the creators of TowerFall, Celeste is a hardcore mountain-climbing platformer coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and Steam in 2017! 

http://www.celestegame.com

Trailer by Kert Gartner, Power Up Audio, and Lena Chappelle.
